			"§ \nMaximize tool performance for customer-specific use cases through deep\ntechnical engagement during NPI and ramp in order to gain customer trust\nand win business\n\n§ \nDevelop, document, proliferate and version manage Apps BKMs for\nhigh quality recipes\n\nApplications engineering requires a\nlarge set of skills\n\n» \nSound fundamentals of high-NA DUV imaging, SEM column physics,\nlight/electron- matter interaction \n\n» \nLab/fab hands-on exp in semiconductor fabrication with detailed\nknowledge of process tech and defectivity\n\n» \nDetail oriented with strong analytical, problem solving and\ncommunication skills\n\n» \nAbility to work in a team, and ability to work independently\n\n» \nBasic knowledge of software scripting, Matlab and image processing\nwill be a plus\n\n» \nOpen to 60% travel overseas",
