		details:
			"🛍️ About MeeshoMeesho started with a bold idea - to make internet commerce accessible to every Indian, everywhere. A decade later, we’ve grown into India’s largest horizontal e-commerce platform for the next billion users - but the mission hasn’t changed: Democratize internet commerce for everyone.Our name - Meri Shop - reflects who we build for: the small business owner in Bharat. Whether it’s a saree seller in Surat, a reseller in Ranchi, or a first-time shopper in a Tier-3 town - we’re their platform of choice. We’ve helped millions of sellers to go online, with zero commission, lowest logistics cost, and a deeply localized, relatable assortment that mirrors how India shops.But we’re more than just an app - we’re a culture of first principles thinking, humility, and high ownership. We’ve built a company that moves fast, thinks long-term, and empowers people to take big bets early in their careers.Our 10-year journey has been one of experimentation, pivots, resilience, and impact. From being India’s top reseller platform to becoming the first Indian e-commerce company to turn profitable, we’ve done what few thought was possible - all while keeping our users and sellers at the heart of every decision.So if you’re looking to build for Bharat, solve complex problems at scale, and be part of a team that values courage over convention - Meesho is the place for you.🎓 About the Role: Senior Associate – Business Management TrackThis is not your average entry-level job.As a Senior Associate, you’ll be thrown into the deep end from Day 1. You’ll get end-to-end exposure to solving 10x problems, owning business charters, working with CXOs, and shaping strategies that directly impact millions of users and sellers across India.You’ll join one of our core business verticals, working in small, high-impact teams. You’ll solve real business challenges, use data like second nature, and move at the speed of a startup.🧠 What You'll Work OnYou'll be mapped to one of the following tracks based on your interest and business needs:1. Category ManagementOwn the P&L of a product category.Design pricing, assortment, and promotions strategies.Decode user behavior and stay ahead of competitionScale categories from 0 to 1 and 1 to 100.2. User GrowthDesign experiments and campaigns to bring millions of new users.Optimize performance marketing and growth loops.Use data to craft insights that shape Meesho’s growth engine.3. Fulfillment & ExperienceSolve for delight across delivery, returns, and support.Improve metrics like delivery TAT, NPS, cancellations, and more.Work with product and ops teams to scale high-efficiency systems.4. Business DevelopmentExpand strategic categories and seller networks.Identify high-potential brand partnerships.Influence long-term strategic direction and team goals.5. MonetizationMake commerce sustainable by driving ads and seller monetization.Conceptualize, pilot, and scale monetization products.Work cross-functionally with product, analytics, and sales teams.🧩 Who Should ApplyFinal year B.Tech students from any streamA curious, analytical mind with strong problem-solving skillsPassion for startups, ownership, and fast-paced workAbility to hustle, work cross-functionally, and influence outcomesExcellent written and verbal communication💰 Compensation & PerksTotal CTC: ₹36.25 LPAFixed Pay: ₹17.25 LPAJoining Bonus: ₹4.75L per year (for 4 years)Perks You’ll Love:📍 Flexible work culture & hybrid setup🍕 Food, fun, and vibrant office spaces🧠 Exposure to leaders & steep learning curve✨ Impact from Day 1 in one of India’s fastest-growing startups🏆 Performance-based growth & ownership🌈 Why Meesho?Because we're not building a company. We're building a movement.Because we don’t care where you come from – we care where you’re headed.Because here, your ideas don’t need ten approvals — just tenacity.Because at Meesho, you’re not just joining a job — you’re launching your entrepreneurial journey.Ready to reimagine Bharat with us?Apply now. Dream big. Hustle hard. Win together.",
