		details:
			"Kotak Data Labs plays a pivotal role in driving\ninnovation and business growth at Kotak. The team collaborates with\nstakeholders and data providers, leveraging advanced analytics and Data Science\n/ Machine Learning techniques to drive strategic decision-making across the\nbank. The core work charter includes supporting different products across the\nbank by developing solutions across the customer journey to drive Acquisition,\nEngagement and Retention using cutting-edge Data Science capabilities and Data\nplatforms.\n\n \n\nThe Data Scientist and Data Analyst role within\nthe team involves deploying projects from conception to actionable insights,\nenabling data-driven marketing strategies, developing risk scorecards, building\nbehavioral models and impact in the banking business. This role focuses on\nleveraging Data science techniques for model development, feature engineering,\ndriving automation, process improvement, and operational efficiency while demonstrating\ninnovative thinking, passion for data science and fostering cross-team\ncollaboration. Establishing strong working relationship with stakeholders in\nthe bank is also a key aspect of this role.\n\nRoles and Responsibilities:\n\n· * Deliver end to end Data Science/Analytics\nprojects including understanding of business requirements, exploratory data\nanalysis, data processing, aggregating data, feature engineering, building and validating\npredictive models, explaining model results & insights and deployment\n\n· * Use AI, ML, DL techniques such as\nregression, classification, clustering, tree-based algorithms, support vector\nmachine, and neural networks, recommender system, attribution modelling to\naddress business problems.\n\n· * Improve upon existing methodologies\nby developing new data sources/features, testing model enhancements, and\nfine-tuning model parameters.\n\n· * Provide requirements to develop\nanalytical capabilities, platforms, and pipelines.\n\n· * Present insights and recommendations\nto audiences of varying levels of technical sophistication\n\n· * Automate processes to ensure\nscalability of solutions by collaborating with cross-functional teams\n\n· * Perform the data extraction,\ntransformations, and loading from the source systems and the data lake to the\nanalytics products using independently developed logic\n\n· * Challenge the status quo with\nentrepreneurial innovation in curating new data sources, elevating analytics\nbeyond data reporting and dashboarding to deliver actionable insights",
