		details:
			"About Us\nICICI Lombard: Shape the Future Us\nSince 2001, ICICI Lombard has grown into India’s leading private general insurer, trusted by\nmillions of customers and powered by 15,000+ employees across 328 branches. At the heart of\nour success is our One IL 1 Team ethos, where behaviours like Growth Mindset, Teamwork,\nand Adaptability unite us to achieve more together.\nWe are reimagining insurance with technology and innovation - from AI-driven claim\nsettlements to digital-first customer experiences and data-led solutions that transform the way\nwe serve. Every employee is empowered to innovate, contribute ideas, and create impact\nbeyond their roles.\nOur culture is built on Diversity, Equity, and Inclusion (DEI). With 26% women in our\nworkforce, generational diversity, and inclusion workshops across India, we ensure equal access\nto opportunities, resources, and leadership pathways.\nWe also take pride in giving back through CSR programs like Caring Hands, Ride to Safety,\nand Niranjali, which have touched millions of lives and earned global recognition, including\ntwo Guinness World Records.\nRecognised as a Great Place to Work six times, featured among the Best Companies for Women\nin India, and globally honoured with ATD Best Awards for 13 years, ICICI Lombard is where\nyou can grow, innovate, and make a difference.\nJoin us - together, we succeed as One IL 1 Team.General Description of the Job\nJob Description: We are looking for a dynamic and experienced individual to join our team as\nSenior Manager - Innovation & Strategy at ICICI Lombard General Insurance. In this role, you\nwill be at the forefront of driving technological advancement and fostering innovation across the\ninsurance landscape. As a Senior Manager, you will play a pivotal role in shaping, leading, and\nexecuting strategic initiatives, with a strong focus on leveraging cutting-edge technologies to\ndesign and develop next-generation insurtech solutions.Role & Responsibilities\n1.Technology Innovation: Lead the development and implementation of AI and ML solutions to enhance multiple\nfacets of insurance operations, including underwriting, risk assessment, and claims\nmanagement. Drive the adoption of Python-based development to build innovative tools, automation\nframeworks, and analytical applications. Spearhead the integration of advanced technologies-such as IoT, GIS, satellite imaging,\nand location-based data into core insurance processes to generate actionable insights for\nrisk assessment and claims processing.\n Evaluate, optimize, and refine existing processes and systems to ensure alignment with\nindustry best practices and to improve operational efficiency.\n2. Collaboration with External Ecosystem:\n Partner with external solution providers and technology partners to identify, evaluate,\nand integrate third-party technologies that support and align with organizational strategic\ngoals.3. Strategic Planning:\n Work closely with senior leadership to develop and execute data-driven business\nstrategies, ensuring alignment with overall business objectives and long-term vision.\n4. Cross-Functional Collaboration:\nCollaborate with multiple internal teams, including IT, Data Science, and Operations, to ensure\nthe seamless integration and adoption of technological solutions across the organization.Education / Additional Requirements\nSkills Required: Expertise in developing and deploying Machine Learning models.\n Strong strategic thinking and analytical capabilities.\n Excellent communication and interpersonal skills.\n Proven ability to lead, guide, and motivate cross-functional teams.\n Ability to thrive in fast-paced, dynamic environments, with a strong focus on process\nand data-driven decision-making.\n Innovative mindset with a passion for staying updated with emerging technologies.\n Experience in Full Stack Development and App Development will be an added\nadvantage\n B.Tech, BS, M.Tech, and M.Sc across all disciplines.\nIf you are passionate about driving innovation in the insurance industry and have a proven track\nrecord in implementing transformative technologies, we encourage you to apply.",
