			"MMA Tech\n\n \n\nMMA Tech is seeking candidates for the following position based\nin the Mumbai/Pune office:\n\n \n\nSenior Software Developer\n\n \n\nWhat can you expect?\n\nIn\nthis role, you will work on software development and support for the company's\nbusiness solutions within a defined Software Development Lifecycle\n\nSupports and assist other developers in\ndeveloping codes, tests and debugs of software programs and enhancements to\nmeet project plan goals.\n\n \n\nWhat is in it for you?\n\n Standard\n MMC Salary Package\n Standard\n MMC Colleague Benefits\n Huge\n landscape to learn & work on new technologies and apply your skills\n\n \n\nWe will count on you to:\n\n· A genuine passion for technology and solving\nproblems\n\n· A pragmatic approach to software development\nand delivery\n\n· Ready to work on technical design and\nsoftware development across multiple technology initiatives.\n\n· Facilitate and help establish software\ndevelopment standards and best practices.\n\n· Working with other developers and tech leads\nto construct a repeatable reusable automation workflow enterprise architecture\nsolution that is scalable, adaptable, and in synch with ever-changing business\nneeds.Work on in-house application build on technologies like\n Python, Dot Net, MEAN stack etc with good knowledge of DBMS/RDBMS/No SQL.\n\n· Participate in code reviews and ensure that\nall solutions are aligned to architectural specifications,\nidentify/troubleshoot application issues.\n\n· Work with Business Analysts, Scrum Masters,\nProduct Owners, and other cross-functional resources to define and deliver\nbusiness impacting projects.\n\n· Collaborate with development team members to\nensure proper implementation and integration of the solutions.\n\n· Support deployments or troubleshoot\nproduction issues outside of work hours and participate in an on-call rotation as\nneeded.\n\n· \nUtilize\nGenerative AI tools to enhance coding efficiency, automate repetitive tasks,\nand improve code quality.\n\n· Maintain current knowledge of relevant\ntechnologies and business processes.\n\n \n\nWhat you’ll get to do:\n\n• \nDesign and build, modern digital applications.\n\n• \nWrite code alongside your development team.\n\n• \nWork with state-of-the-art technologies to solve genuine, real-world\nproblems.\n\n• \nBuild strong relationships with other tech teams.\n\n• \nEnjoy working in a diverse, dynamic, collaborative, transparent,\nenvironment where everyone's ideas and opinions are equally valued.\n\n \n\nWhat you need to have: \n\n At\n least one software project experience as an intern, college project, or\n self-initiative using any of the mentioned technologies.\n Strong\n fundamentals of programming language (Understanding of OOPS principles) \n\n· AppDev: JavaScript, Dot Net\nand/or MEAN stack\n\n· Data: Python, BI &\nReporting\n\n Good\n knowledge of DBMS/RDBMS/No SQL (Mongo) – Strong SQL and/or PLSQL\n fundamentals\n Excellent\n analytical and logical thinking skills.\n Strong\n problem-solving skills with a goal-oriented mindset.\n Interest\n and ability to quickly learn new technology stacks and programming\n languages.\n Mandatory\n knowledge of multithreading programming.\n Familiar\n with AzureDevops Tools set will be an advantage.\n Knowledge\n of LLMs and prompt engineering techniques\n\n· \nMust be familiar with version\ncontrol tools like GitHub.\n\n Must be\n familiar to Agile software development practices \n\n \n\nWhat makes you stand out?\n\n· \nExcellent\ncommunication and presentation skills\n\n· \nAbility to multitask\nand liaise with multiple stakeholders\n\n· \nStrong interpersonal\nskills and demonstrated ability to build professional relationships\n\n· \nExcellent Problem-solving\nskills with innovative and proactive approach\n\n· \nAbility to identify\nprocess improvement opportunities\n\n· \nAdaptability to\nchange\n\n· \nKnowledge of\nprocesses & best practices within the team & industry",
