			"What You’ll Work On ● AI Research: Forecasting models, retail foundation LLMs, and patent-worthy\ninnovations.\n● Agentic AI: Build Agent Studio, Agent Platform-as-a-Service, and autonomous agents\nthat reason, act, and collaborate.\n● Advanced Computing: Next-gen data platforms, in-memory engines, distributed\nsystems at terabyte scale, even quantum computing explorations.\n● Engineering Tools: Developer-first frameworks (SmartGrid, orchestration engines)\nthat empower 300+ engineers.Why You’ll Love It ● Work side by side with senior architects and engineering leaders as part of the CTO’s\noffice\n● Contribute to IP and patents from Day 1.\n● Build tech that powers operations at massive scale for global enterprises.\n● Exposure to cutting-edge stacks: Rust, TypeScript, DuckDB, Spark, Kubernetes,\nMLFlow, Kubeflow, BigQuery/Snowflake, Terraform.\n● Fast-cycle culture: Prototype → Optimize → Scale.\nWhat We’re Looking For\n● Passionate coders and problem solvers (Python, Rust, TypeScript, C++, Java).\n● Curious minds who love AI/ML, distributed systems, or advanced computing.\n● Builders who want to work on real problems at massive scale.\n● People who are excited to research, innovate, and leave a mark.",
