		details:
			"Job Description - Software Developer (Fresh Graduate)Why would you like to join us?TransOrg Analytics specializes in Data Science, Data Engineering and Generative AI, providing advancedanalytics solutions to industry leaders and Fortune 500 companies across India, US, APAC and the MiddleEast. We leverage data science to streamline, optimize, and accelerate our clients' businesses. Visit atwww.transorg.com to know more about us.What do we expect from you?We are looking for enthusiastic Software Developers with strong problem-solving and analyticalskills. As part of our development team, you will design and build scalable web applications, APIs,and AI/ML-driven services. This role offers an opportunity to learn modern technologies (MERNstack, Python-FastAPI, cloud deployments) while working on real-world business problems.In this role, you will:● Learn to design and build end-to-end web applications.● Contribute to developing APIs and integrating AI/ML models with real-world applications.● Collaborate with data teams, business users, and mentors to deliver impactful solutions.● Gain hands-on experience in cloud deployments, CI/CD pipelines, and service integrationsacross platforms.Key Responsibilities● Backend Development○ Learn and build scalable backend services and RESTful APIs usingNode.js and Express.○ Collaborate with data and Gen AI teams to integrate APIs,models, and pipelines.○ Gain exposure to FastAPI (Python) for service integrations andbackend utilities.● Frontend Development○ Develop intuitive and responsive user interfaces using React.○ Apply modern UI/UX principles to create user-centric webapplications.● Database & Storage○ Design and work with schemas using MongoDB or SQL/NoSQLdatabases.○ Manage data interactions for file-based inputs using cloudstorage solutions (e.g., Azure Blob Storage).● Cloud Deployment & DevOps○ Contribute to deploying and maintaining applications on AzureApp Service (or similar).○ Gain working knowledge of Docker and Containerization.○ Learn and support CI/CD pipeline configurations andenvironment setup.○ Exposure to Azure Pipelines is a plus.● Collaboration & Code Quality○ Work closely with analysts, product stakeholders, and mentors todeliver solutions.○ Follow clean coding practices and participate in code reviews tolearn and improve quality.● Testing & Debugging○ Write basic unit and integration tests to ensure stability.○ Troubleshoot and resolve issues with guidance from seniordevelopers.What are we looking for?● Education: B.Tech / B.E. / M.Tech / MCA / M.Sc. in Computer Science, IT, orrelated fields.● Core Skills:○ Strong problem-solving and logical thinking abilities.○ Solid understanding of Data Structures, Algorithms, and OOPsconcepts.○ Good knowledge of web technologies (HTML, CSS, JavaScript).○ Familiarity with at least one programming language (JavaScript,Python, Java, C++).● Preferred Skills (Good to have, not mandatory):○ Exposure to frameworks like React, Node.js, or FastAPI.○ Awareness of databases (SQL/NoSQL).○ Curiosity to explore AI/ML and cloud technologies.● Soft Skills:○ Willingness to learn new technologies quickly.○ Good communication and teamwork skills.○ Ability to adapt to dynamic project requirements.If you are curious about how AI, data, and web technologies come together to solvereal-world problems, we invite you to be part of our team and shape innovativesolutions with us.",
