		details:
			"As an SDE, you will work on high-impact distributed systems powering automated financial solutions for supply chains. You will collaborate with founders, customers, and team leads to shape and execute product strategy. Your responsibilities include building across the full tech stack—designing APIs, creating optimized schemas, developing data pipelines, and setting up cloud infrastructure with automated deployments. You will own end-to-end design and implementation of key features, enhance backend API performance, write detailed documentation, and ensure code quality through comprehensive unit test cases. This role offers significant ownership, technical depth, and direct product impact.",
