			"Resume filtering | Round 1 (01:00) | Round 2 (01:00) | Round 3 (01:00) | Round 4 (01:00)",
		details:
			"About NAKADNAKAD is a 4-year-old AI startup backed by Accel and Matrix Partners, and has raised one of India’s largest early-stage rounds.Founded by alumni of IIM Ahmedabad, IIT Bombay, and IIT Guwahati, with experience across BCG, HUL, Samsung, and Oracle, NAKAD is building AI agents that transform Finance and Accounting for companies in the US.We sit at the intersection of AI + FinOps, helping global brands automate some of their most complex workflows — from reconciliations and deductions to end-to-end accounting close.Our journey so far:🏆 Winner — TiE Best Startup in India🏅 Featured in SutraHR Top 100 Startups in India🌎 Trusted by 170+ brands, expanding rapidly in the US market💡 Backed by top global investors, product-first culture, and relentless speedAt NAKAD, we value hustle, ownership, and energy. We move fast, build iteratively, and work shoulder-to-shoulder with clients solving real problems — not from behind dashboards.RoleWe are hiring sharp, high-ownership graduates to drive product and implementation end-to-end.You’ll work directly with finance leaders at US-based CPG brands, understand their workflows, change the product and ensure our AI systems are configured, tested, and adopted successfully.This is not a back-office role - it’s frontline execution with deep learning, combining analytics, product thinking, and client empathy.What You’ll DoOwn the end-to-end product and client implementation journey - from product changes to go-live.Translate client needs into structured workflows and collaborate with product/engineering to solve them fast.Bring energy and speed - find problems, fix them, and move.What You’ll Need1. Exceptional problem-solving and analytical skills.2. High ownership and hunger to learn — you take responsibility, not just tasks.3. Strong communication and client-facing ability.4. Thrive in fast-paced, ambiguous environments; enjoy wearing multiple hats.5. Interest in AI, finance, or startups is a plus (we’ll teach you the rest).What You’ll Get🚀 Front-row seat in building a category-defining AI company in the US💼 Direct mentorship from founders and senior leaders🧠 Steep learning curve — exposure to product, AI, and enterprise clients early in your career🔥 High ownership + fast growth — your performance directly shapes NAKAD’s US success🌍 Global exposure — work with US clients, products, and processesLocation: GurugramCompensation: Competitive + performance incentives",
