		details:
			"Department Brief:At NSE, we pride ourselves on fostering innovation and solving complex challenges through cutting-edge technology. We are \nseeking dynamic and motivated fresh graduates to join our Tech ADM team. This role offers exposure to both front-end and \nback-end technologies and provides an opportunity to work on end-to-end delivery of projects in collaboration with \nexperienced professionals. \nYou will be part of a high-performing team focused on building scalable, secure, and customer-centric solutions across digital \nplatforms including mobile and web, ensuring an omni-channel experience for end users. \nData Warehousing & Analytics team of NSE is responsible, among other things for establishing and managing the Data \nWarehouse Solution including Designing, Architecture, Development of Analytical Solutions primarily for captive \nconsumption. This includes creation and maintenance of our database infrastructure, including collecting and maintaining \ndata, ensuring the integrity of our data, and creating and training data models. The Exchange is the convergence of the 3 Is – \nInvestors, Intermediaries and Issuers. Role and Responsibilities:• Develop and maintain scalable, distributed systems and responsive applications. • Collaborate with cross-functional teams to define, design, and deliver robust solutions. • Translate business and user requirements into technical specifications. • Participate in the full software development lifecycle (SDLC) including design, development, testing, and \ndeployment. • Conduct code reviews and ensure high standards of code quality and design. • Identify risks and deviations proactively and communicate effectively with stakeholders.",
