		details:
			"About the Role\n\nWe are looking for a highly motivated Full Stack Software\nDeveloper with expertise in Next.js, React.js, and TypeScript to\njoin our team. You will be working on building a cutting-edge platform designed\nto create and manage investment portfolios. This role is ideal for\nsomeone who is passionate about fintech, thrives in fast-paced environments,\nand is eager to take ownership of their work.\n\nKey Responsibilities\n\n· \nDesign, develop, and maintain\nscalable web applications using Next.js, React.js, and TypeScript.\n\n· \nCollaborate with product and\nbusiness teams to transform requirements into technical solutions.\n\n· \nTake accountability for\ndelivery of assigned tasks and modules, ensuring high-quality, timely\nreleases.\n\n· \nIntegrate APIs and third-party\nservices to enhance platform functionality.\n\n· \nWrite clean, maintainable, and\nwell-documented code.\n\n· \nCommunicate clearly about\nprogress, hurdles, delays, and technical challenges.\n\n· \nParticipate in code reviews,\ntesting, and deployment pipelines.\n\n· \nContribute to architectural\ndecisions and scalability planning as the platform grows.\n\nExpectations\n\n· \nStrong sense of discipline\nin daily tasks and ability to manage work independently.\n\n· \nTransparent and communicative\nabout issues, delays, and blockers.\n\n· \nCommitment to building a\nrobust, reliable, and user-friendly investment portfolio platform.\n\nSkills & Qualifications\n\n· \nProficiency in Next.js,\nReact.js, TypeScript.\n\n· \nStrong understanding of REST\nAPIs and modern web architectures.\n\n· \nExperience with Docker\nfor containerization and deployment.\n\n· \nFamiliarity with using Generative\nAI coding tools (e.g., Claude Code, Roo Code, or similar) to accelerate\ndevelopment.\n\n· \nFamiliarity with Firebase\nservices for authentication, hosting, or real-time data.\n\n· \nExperience with databases\n(SQL/NoSQL).\n\n· \nKnowledge of secure coding\npractices and authentication/authorization flows.\n\n· \nGood problem-solving skills and\nattention to detail.\n\nWhat We Offer\n\n· \nA dynamic, collaborative work\nenvironment where your contributions directly impact business success.\n\n· \nGrowth opportunities in a\nfintech venture shaping the future of investment management.\n\n· \nAccess to the latest tools,\ntechnologies, and resources to accelerate your development.\n\n· \nA culture of learning,\ninnovation, and continuous improvement.",
		info: "Compensation Structure\n\n· \nBasic Salary: ₹1,00,000 per month.\n\n· \nProbation Period: First 3 months at ₹50,000 per month.\n\n· \nProbation Completion Bonus: On successful completion of probation, an additional ₹1,50,000\nwill be paid at the end of 3 months, and salary will move to ₹1,00,000 per\nmonth.\n\n· \nNotice Period: 2 weeks during probation, 1 month post probation.\n\n· \nAnnual Bonus: Eligible for up to ₹3,00,000 performance-based bonus upon\ncompleting one year.\n\n· \nESOP Options: Opportunity to receive large ESOP grants after one year of\nsuccessful contribution.",
