			"As an Associate Supply Chain Consultant at Lyric.tech, you will play a key role in supporting\nclient engagements focused on supply chain transformation and digital enablement. The role\ncombines data-driven problem solving, process design, and technology implementation to\ndeliver measurable business outcomes. Key Responsibilities: ● Support supply chain strategy, planning, and transformation projects across industries.● Analyze operational data and identify opportunities for cost optimization, improved\nefficiency, and agility.● Assist in process diagnostics, benchmarking, and solution design. ● Work on implementation of ERP and SCM tools such as SAP, Oracle, Kinaxis, or Blue\nYonder. ● Prepare client deliverables including reports, dashboards, and executive presentations.● Collaborate with cross-functional client and internal teams across operations,\nprocurement, finance, and logistics.● Stay updated on global supply chain trends and emerging technologies.",
