		details:
			"Larsen\n & Toubro (L&T) believes that building extraordinary infrastructure,\n engineering solutions, and technological innovations begins with building\n extraordinary leaders. The Management Trainee (MT) Program is a strategic\n initiative to identify, develop, and nurture high-potential talent who will\n contribute as future leaders of the organization. The program offers exposure\n to strategic and challenging business projects, supported by a structured\n learning journey that blends on-the-job experiences with formal learning\n interventions. This program is designed for accelerated career progression,\n empowering trainees to take on impactful responsibilities early in their\n careers.\n \n As part of the Management Trainee Program, selected MTs will gain exposure\n to challenging projects, structured learning interventions, and fast-tracked\n career growth opportunities. The program also includes a one-year structured\n mentorship initiative called MPower, where each trainee will be a part of a\n guided mentoring relationship with a Senior Leader at L&T, MTs develop\n strong leadership capabilities alongside their technical skills, gaining\n practical insights and professional direction that prepare them for future\n leadership roles at L&T.\n \n If you are driven by purpose, passionate about tackling real-world\n challenges, and eager to learn from some of the finest minds in engineering\n and management, L&T offers an empowering platform to lead, innovate, and\n grow. Join us to build the future—and shape your own leadership journey with\n impact.",
