		details:
			"Job Description\n\nCompany Name- Xion Multiventures Pvt.Ltd.\n(ARB Trading Group)\n\nAbout Company- \n\nXion Multiventures Pvt Ltd is a leading company providing research and\nconsultancy services backed by back-office operations working in capital\nmarkets. Xion Multiventures Pvt. Ltd. is a wholly-owned subsidiary of ARB TG, a\nproprietary firm having offices in Canada, U.S, U.K., Poland, Israel and\nUkraine. ARB TG provides a professional trading environment, infrastructure and\ncapital to support traders across the globe. ARB TG (Xion Multiventures Pvt\nLtd) is united by an entrepreneurial spirit rooted in a mission to develop\nsuccessful traders and created a dynamic culture fostering traders personal and\nprofessional growth. ARB TG addresses the individual needs of the trader. With a\nhands-on approach, ARB TG (Xion Multiventures Pvt Ltd) encourages a broader\nworld experience by offering traders the opportunity to trade from any of ARB’s\nglobal offices. Remaining in lockstep with the technological changes sweeping\nthe financial markets and going beyond their own borders, ARB TG (Xion\nMultiventures Pvt Ltd) has been empowering traders since its inception.\n\n \n\n#Job Description–The job\ninvolves research analysis and execution service of futures & options in\nEuropean and US exchanges and presents a unique opportunity to Indian individuals\nto work in the exotic field of Derivatives in the world’s most liquid and\nwell-developed markets.\n\n \n\n#Eligiblity Criteria\n\nStudents\nadmitted through JEE Above 6.5 CGPA\n\nFinal year appearing students who can join\nus from June 2026\n\n \n\nNo. of Vacancies\n(approximate)-6 Place of Posting- Hyderabad",
