			"Job Description for Assistant\nProfessor Role:\n\nWe\nare seeking passionate and committed Assistant Professors to join our Amrita University\nFaculty team. The role involves teaching, guiding students, conducting\nimpactful research, and contributing to academic excellence in your field of\nexpertise.Key Responsibilities:Deliver\nengaging lectures for undergraduate and postgraduate students.Guide\nstudent projects, internships, and research work.Publish\nresearch in reputed journals and conferences.Develop\nand update course materials to meet industry and academic standards.Participate\nin departmental and university activities.\n\nQualifications:Ph.D in the relevant discipline (exceptional candidates with other qualifications\nmay be considered. Strong\nacademic and research track record. Excellent communication and mentoring skills.",
