		details:
			"Job Title: Software Development Engineer Location: BengaluruEmployment Type: Full-TimeDepartment: Engineering / TechnologyAbout the Role:We are looking for passionate, driven, and highly motivated Software Development Engineers (SDEs) to join our dynamic team. As an SDE, you will work on designing, developing, testing, and deploying scalable software solutions. You can specialize in Frontend, Backend, or work across the Full Stack, depending on your strengths and interests.This is an excellent opportunity for recent graduates who want to kick-start their career in a fast-paced and technology-driven environment.Key Responsibilities:Skills Required:• Collaborate with design, product, and QA teams.• Write clean, maintainable code; participate in code reviews.• Contribute to the full software development lifecycle.• Debug, test, and optimize for performance.Technical Requirements:Frontend: HTML, CSS, JS, React/Angular/Vue, GitBackend: Java/Python/Node.js, Express/Django/Spring Boot, REST APIs, SQL/NoSQLWhat We Offer:• Mentorship & learning opportunities• Friendly and collaborative work culture• Growth-driven roles and flexible workingWhat’s in it for you?At Mygate you can-• Work in a setting that encourages collaboration and trust, enabling you to put your ideas into action.• Be a member of an effective team where everyone's input countMygate Values:Innovation | Speed | Excellence | Customer Obsession | Confidentiality | Collaboration | FrugalityDisclaimer: Mygate is an Equal Opportunity Employer and takes pride in maintaining a diverse environment. We do not discriminate in recruitment, hiring, training, promotion, or other employment practices for reasons of race, colour, religion, gender, age, sexual orientation gender identity, marital status, disability, or any reason",
