			"Job Description: We are looking for a passionate and talented Software Development Engineer (SDE) with astrong interest in product development to join our dynamic team. As an employee, you will play akey role in building new features and improving the performance, reliability, and scalability of oured-tech platform. This is a unique opportunity to gain hands-on experience in a fast-pacedstart-up environment, working alongside experienced engineers, designers, and productmanagers.Key Responsibilities:• Develop and maintain scalable web applications and backend APIs.• Enhance and build custom compilers and contribute to the evolution of our internalcompiler tools.• Improve and extend core systems such as the proctoring platform and AI-drivenfunctionalities.• Design and implement new features and product enhancements across the tech stack.• Write clean, efficient, and maintainable code, following best practices and codingstandards.• Participate in code reviews, identify bugs, and help with debugging and performanceoptimization.• Collaborate closely with UI/UX designers, product managers, and other developers todeliver seamless user experiences.Requirements:• Currently pursuing under graduation - All.• Proficiency in either of the following tech stacks:• Frontend: JavaScript, HTML, CSS, React, and Redux• Backend: Python with Django, or Golang• Familiarity with Git and version control systems.• Strong problem-solving skills with a keen attention to detail.• Effective communication skills and the ability to collaborate in a team-oriented environment.Preferred Qualifications:• Previous internship experience or personal projects using React or Django.• Strong foundation in Data Structures and Algorithms (DSA).• Familiarity with AI-powered coding assistants (e.g., GitHub Copilot, Cursor, Claude Code).• Experience working with testing frameworks (e.g., Jest, PyTest, Go test).What We Offer:• A collaborative and inclusive work environment that fosters learning and innovation.• Hands-on experience working on real-world projects that directly impact our platform andusers.• Mentorship and guidance from experienced engineers and product leaders.• Flexible working hours.",
