			"Roles & Responsibilities:§ Execute R&D projects in “Process Modelling & Scale up” area of Cement Domain.§ Visit the plant/customer to gather information about the process and process equipment.§ Carry out simulations/data analytics and validations with plant data. Interpretation of simulations and experimental results & data for root cause analysis.§ Develop expert solutions for the respective projects with effective collaborations across cross-functional teams, adherence to timelines and budget.§ Implementation of technical solutions in the plant.§ Publish/present in National/International Journals/Conferences.Skills:§ Knowledge of Process modelling using Computational Fluid Dynamics (CFD) or ASPEN.§ Fundamental understanding of the principals of fluid dynamics/ reaction engineering/ combustion/ heat and mass transfer and multiphase turbulent fluid problems.§ Good Communication and Presentation skills.Good to Have:§ Knowledge in Data visualization, statistical analysis & Data Analytics with AI ML modelling.§ Writing own codes in MATLAB, R, Python§ knowledge of scientific, high-performance and cloud computing tools and technologies Qualification & Experience:§ M.E/M.Tech in Chemical Engineering",
