		details:
			'Company Description: Honda is a total mobility company dedicated to delivering the "joy of free movement." We innovate in various fields, including motorcycles, automobiles, power products, aircraft and aircraft engines, and robotics. Honda operates in markets across about 200 countries worldwide, continuously creating next-generation mobility solutions and products that improve people’s lives by combining our technology and expertise.At Honda, everyone, regardless of nationality, gender, educational background, or experience, can freely express their ideas. Since our founding, we have maintained the ambition of asking, "What can we do for the world and for people?"We believe that having dreams and staying passionate about making them a reality is the reason Honda exists. "It\'s not about what happens; it\'s about what you do." You are the ones who will shape the future of the world. As you move forward in life, we hope you will be the main character in the moments when the world changes.If you have a desire to achieve something, to create something, or to make your dreams come true, why not realize those aspirations at Honda?Domain Description: 〈Software Defined Vehicle Business Development Unit, Digital Engine Development Division〉At Honda, The Power of Dreams inspires us to create intelligent, connected products that enhance mobility and bring joy to people’s lives. Our goal is to deliver affordable, AI-powered solutions that make customers smile—by combining cutting-edge technology, ethical transparency, and collaborative innovation. The automotive industry is undergoing a profound transformation. Vehicles are evolving from mere modes of transportation into intelligent, connected platforms that deliver new value to customers. To lead this shift, Honda is accelerating its efforts to build AI service platforms, develop core AI technologies, and create a data-driven development environment where data becomes a strategic asset for the entire organization. We are pioneering technical processes that enable rapid value validation, allowing us to test and deploy advanced AI technologies with speed and agility.Our team is global, highly motivated, and committed to shaping the future of mobility. We are now seeking new colleagues to help us explore the next generation of intelligent products and services. Your energy and creativity will help drive innovation forward. As part of this mission, we are advancing a Honda-style SDV (Software-Defined Vehicle) intelligence strategy, focused on building cost-effective AI development environments and strengthening partnerships around core technologies. Our diverse team already includes around 10 IIT graduates contributing their expertise.We are currently looking for an innovative scientist with a strong background in Artificial Intelligence. Honda generates vast amounts of vehicle and customer data, and in this role, you will lead both technological research and real-world product development using this data. In this position, you won’t just be a scientist—you will act as a product owner, project manager, and business innovator. You’ll develop and release AI-based services and continuously refine them through customer and vehicle feedback.We value ambition, motivation, and a proactive approach to learning. Strong communication skills and a collaborative mindset are essential. We also hope you’ll connect with Honda’s founding philosophy and help us bring it to life in everything we do.To support this vision, we are building training programs and promoting research themes worthy of academic publication, ensuring our team is prepared to compete on the global stage.Job Description:■Position / Job Description• Participate in existing projects and learn Honda\'s business processes, key stakeholders, and philosophy to eventually become an independent project leader.• Identify both existing and new research problems by interacting with Honda team members. Help refine research methodology by sharing research trends and best practices within the community.• Actively collaborate with business, product, marketing, UX, and other internal stakeholders to create functional requirements and propose new projects that could be of value to customers.• Develop new algorithms for the utilization of AI both outside and inside the car using various sensors.• Define the data structure, framework, design, and evaluation metrics for research solution development and implementation.• Drive R&D projects toward strategic product decisions through quick iterations of experimentation and PoC.• Manage all project planning and execution from the launch of the project to the delivery of the product to the customer.• Author research papers and apply for patents to share and generate impact from research results across the team and within the research community.• Perform basic project management routines including scheduling, cost management, stakeholder relationship management, and service health and performance monitoring.■Key Highlights・A new software studio and stylish office in a modern city.・Development of actual AI-powered consumer services that will be used by Honda customers.・Access to real vehicles and vehicle data as Honda’s proprietary assets.',
