			'Company Description: Honda is a total mobility company dedicated to delivering the "joy of free movement." We innovate in various fields, including motorcycles, automobiles, power products, aircraft and aircraft engines, and robotics. Honda operates in markets across about 200 countries worldwide, continuously creating next-generation mobility solutions and products that improve people’s lives by combining our technology and expertise.At Honda, everyone, regardless of nationality, gender, educational background, or experience, can freely express their ideas. Since our founding, we have maintained the ambition of asking, "What can we do for the world and for people?"We believe that having dreams and staying passionate about making them a reality is the reason Honda exists. "It\'s not about what happens; it\'s about what you do." You are the ones who will shape the future of the world. As you move forward in life, we hope you will be the main character in the moments when the world changes.If you have a desire to achieve something, to create something, or to make your dreams come true, why not realize those aspirations at Honda?Domain Description: 〈Software Defined Mobility Development Supervisory Unit, Advanced Safety and Intelligent Solution Development Division〉Honda\'s Software Defined Mobility Development Supervisory Unit is committed to pursuing innovative development and creation of “value” in mobility and life. We aim for “Zero traffic collision fatalities” involving Honda motorcycles or automobiles worldwide in 2050. The AD/ADAS division is responsible for the development of safety functions such as Honda Sensing Elite and Honda sensing 360 for this purpose. In this division, the engineers who realized the world\'s first LV3 automated driving system are constantly researching and commercializing the latest technologies.Our mission is to develop world-leading safety features and autonomous driving systems and to deliver the safest vehicles in the world. This represents a significant shift from conventional automobiles and demands innovation, particularly through the application of AI technologies. It is a field that requires deep technical exploration and a spirit of challenge.We offer an environment where you can engage in global research and development in collaboration with Honda’s overseas offices, universities, and companies. We are looking for teammates who possess specialized technologies that contribute to major transformations and innovations in mobility—and who are eager not only to conduct research but also to bring their work into the real world and make a meaningful contribution to society.Job Description: You will be responsible for developing one or more of the following technologies related to next-generation development of driver assistance and autonomous driving systems:- Image recognition algorithms and machine learning models for object and lane recognition- Traffic environment understanding algorithms and machine learning models using recognition data- Behavior planning algorithms and machine learning models based on traffic conditions- Edge device deployment of machine learning models - Multimodal fusion technologies using cameras and other external sensing devices- Driver state and in-cabin recognition using DNNs and LLMs- Self-localization and automated map generation - MLOps environment construction- Optimization, probabilistic inference, and data miningYou will also be involved in R&D of AI-based functions for autonomous vehicles, as well as promoting joint research and development with universities and domestic/overseas companies.You will collaborate with various stakeholders, including other departments and vendors. There may also be opportunities to engage with overseas entities, such as demonstrations for local subsidiaries and joint research with international institutions.*Depending on your expertise, aptitude, and company needs, you may be reassigned to other duties as defined by the company.',
