		details:
			'Company Description: Honda is a total mobility company dedicated to delivering the "joy of free movement." We innovate in various fields, including motorcycles, automobiles, power products, aircraft and aircraft engines, and robotics. Honda operates in markets across about 200 countries worldwide, continuously creating next-generation mobility solutions and products that improve people’s lives by combining our technology and expertise.At Honda, everyone, regardless of nationality, gender, educational background, or experience, can freely express their ideas. Since our founding, we have maintained the ambition of asking, "What can we do for the world and for people?"We believe that having dreams and staying passionate about making them a reality is the reason Honda exists. "It\'s not about what happens; it\'s about what you do." You are the ones who will shape the future of the world. As you move forward in life, we hope you will be the main character in the moments when the world changes.If you have a desire to achieve something, to create something, or to make your dreams come true, why not realize those aspirations at Honda?Domain Description: 〈Software Defined Mobility Development Supervisory Unit, Advanced Safety and Intelligent Solution Development Division〉Our mission is to develop world-leading safety features and autonomous driving systems, and to deliver the safest vehicles in the world. Honda\'s AD/ADAS Data Platform Group provides an ecosystem for AD/ADAS system development to analyze and test safety and functionality through simulations, insight and analysis of sensing data from test vehicles. The ecosystem is used in the critical process of validating the results of functional development and obtaining “type certification”. In this division, the engineers who developed the world’s first Level 3 automated driving system are continuously researching and commercializing cutting-edge technologies. Through the development of Level 3 autonomous driving systems, Honda has gained access to valuable market data from both customer and test vehicles. This data is utilized to improve safety validation, product planning, and functional design. The results of your analysis will be applied globally through Honda’s extensive international network, contributing to the realization of a society with zero traffic fatalities.To increase the number of people who smile through their experience with cars, we are seeking teammates who will lead Honda’s global four-wheel development—from foundational product development optimized for each region to cutting-edge technology innovation. As of July 2025, there are currently 10 Indian engineers and 2 Chinese engineers on the team. An additional 6 engineers—all graduates of IIT (Indian Institutes of Technology)—are scheduled to join in October 2025.Employees who proactively engage with their work and demonstrate strong initiative are entrusted with major responsibilities, even shortly after joining. We welcome individuals with the drive to raise their hand and launch projects with the spirit of “I want to create this kind of technology!”Job Description: Our mission is to develop world-class safety features and autonomous driving systems to deliver the safest vehicles worldwide. By utilizing market data from customer vehicles and development vehicle data collected through Honda’s Level 3 autonomous driving system development, you will play a key role in safety validation, product planning, and functional design.【Job Details】 You will be responsible for advanced data analysis to support the next-generation development of driver assistance and autonomous driving systems:- Analyze real-world test data and probe data to extract insights that drive the development of autonomous driving and driver assistance technologies.- Implement advanced analytics and automation funcationalities, inclduing ML and Gen-AI techniques for intelligent data analysis.- Analyze simulation data to support MILS development operations and the development of AD/ADAS models.You will collaborate with a wide range of stakeholders, including internal departments and external vendors. There may also be opportunities to work with overseas teams, such as conducting demonstrations for local subsidiaries or engaging in joint research with international institutions. Specific tasks will be assigned based on your experience and skills. Depending on your expertise, aptitude, and company requirements, you may be reassigned to other duties as defined by the company.【Development Tools】Languages: R, Python, SQLData Analysis / AI Libraries: numpy, scipy, scikit-learn, Jupyter Notebook, PyTorchGen-AI: VLM/LLM, RAG pipelines, Agentic Frameworks (LangChain, CrewAI). Protocols (MCP)Simulation Tools: Matlab/Simulink, CarMaker, CarlaCloud: AWS(Amazon SageMaker, Amazon Athena, Amazon Redshift), GCP, AzureCI/CD: Git, DockerCRM Tools & Integration: Salesforce, Sentiment analysis, Predictive analysis',
