		details:
			"Company Description: Over the years Honda has consistently created new value and contributed to the joy of living. In every activity, Honda considers what it can do for the people of the world living with hope for a bright future, as well as for the Earth and Society. Honda R&D exists as an agency of Honda and leads the activities of research and development. With a history of more than half a century of cutting-edge research and products, we have accumulated a vast wealth of various technologies and knowledge which we believe must be utilized to actively contribute to people, the earth, and society. Our mission for the generations to come is providing new mobility and services while also constantly developing and researching the leading technologies of the times. Honda R&D is embarking on new challenges for the future in a variety of fields and we want you to be a part of this journey. Domain Description: 〈Honda R&D Innovative Research Excellence, Semiconductor Research〉Honda aims to achieve carbon neutrality and zero traffic fatalities by 2050 in all products and corporate activities. In addition to the joy of driving and the joy of free movement that Honda has pursued since its founding, we need electrification technology, AD/ADAS technology, and AI technology for automobiles, which has been increasingly used in various situations in recent years. Traditionally, mechanical hardware, such as internal combustion engine, has been the main factor determining the value of a vehicle. However recently, in SDV (Software Defined Vehicle), the value of electronic platforms that incorporate software has increased. In particular, next-generation logic semiconductors that handle AI have a significant impact on the functional value of electronic platforms. Until now, Honda has procured logic semiconductors that execute AI from external suppliers. In order to increase the value of next-generation electric vehicles, we need to work toward collaborative optimization of AI software and logic semiconductors hardware. We have begun R & D on logic semiconductors that can run AI, including AD/ADAS, at low power and high speed for optimal use in Honda products.Specifically, we conduct R & D on next-generation logic semiconductors from requirements specification definition to architecture design, logical design, physical design, evaluation, prototyping, and verification. We also conduct research on AI models that are optimal for next-generation logic semiconductors and develop middleware such as SDKs and compilers, allowing us to be involved in attractive R & D activities that strongly link hardware and software.Job Description: <Role> Our group works by leveraging the strengths of each member with diverse backgrounds, including the internal task force members who lead Honda's semiconductor development, as well as those experienced in AI development for autonomous driving and other areas. You will work in collaboration with semicondutor hardware development teams and AI function software teams to realize the common goal of creating world-first technologies that can contribute to society.<Specific Goals> [1st -2nd year] You will work on either semiconductor hardware development or AI algorithm development based on your present skillset and your desire to learn new things. By working in a collaborative fashion with different teams in our group you will be building up your knowledge on both hardware and software aspects as well as linking them in optimal fashion.[3rd -5th year] You will be working on unique hardware and software intertwined problems from identification to solution implemention by taking advantage of the expertise and skillset you have developed.",
