		details:
			"Designation: Assistant Structural Design Engineer- BridgesWe are looking for a candidate who wants to be the best Bridge Design Engineer in the world. About CompanyVohra Structural Consultants Private Limited is an Infrastructure Consulting Firm based in Mumbai, India, specialising in creative solutions for complex infrastructural engineering projects. We offer a wide range of consultancy services, including Highway Design, Bridge Design, Geotechnical Reports, and MEP works. Our team of highly qualified and experienced engineering consultants strives for innovation and excellence in every project to provide maximum value for our clients. Role DescriptionWe are seeking a skilled Structural Engineer to join our team, specialising in the design and development of bridges and other infrastructure projects. The ideal candidate will have to work on the following: Bridge Sub-structure foundation designBridge Super-structure designDesign of CulvertsRetaining wall design, Drain design, etc.Foot Over Bridge (FOB) designDesign of stations and related infrastructureCalculation of quantities and preparation of Bill of Quantities (BOQs)Coordination with drafting teams for the successful submission of drawingsInteraction with the geotechnical team for project assessments QualificationsM-Tech in Structural Engineering from IIT or equivalent.Proficiency in using engineering software such as Midas Civil, STAAD.Pro, Sofistik, Lusas, AutoCAD, and Civil 3D.Strong understanding of Structural Analysis and Structural Engineering skillsStrong understanding of bridge designStrong problem-solving and analytical skillsExcellent communication and teamwork abilities Why Join Us?Work on Landmark Projects: Contribute to large-scale, high-impact infrastructure projects that shape the future of transportation and our nation.Cutting-Edge Technologies: Access to the latest in engineering software and technologies that will push the boundaries of your skills and professional growth.Collaborative & Dynamic Environment: Join a passionate, forward-thinking team of professionals where your ideas and contributions matter.Professional Development: Continuous learning and development opportunities to advance your career and stay at the forefront of bridge design.",
