		details:
			"About Smart Analytica:\n\nBased in Pune, Smart Analytica specialize in Data, AI\nand Advanced Analytics domain. Our key focus is on Data and Cloud\nimplementations, Generative AI, Data Modernization, Big Data Cloud Engineering\nand Machine Learning. Our expertise spans state-of-the-art technologies,\nincludes Hadoop, Bigdata, LLM, Generative AI, RAG, Model Building, Big Data\ntech like Apache Spark, Cloudera, Kafka, Google Cloud, AWS, and Azure, enabling\nus to transform enterprise data into actionable insights. \n\nWe have executed numerous data modernization programs,\nhandling up to 24 petabytes of data for the fifth-largest stock exchange in the\nworld, featuring a 160+ node Hadoop cluster, processing over 1 million records\nper second.\n\nAbout the Role:\n\nWe are seeking highly\nmotivated graduates with strong mathematical and programming skills to join our\nData & AI team. This role is ideal for individuals passionate about Artificial\nIntelligence, Data Platforms, and Cloud Technologies, and eager to build\ninnovative solutions that drive business impact.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n\n Assist in designing and developing AI/ML\n models and data-driven solutions.\n Work on data collection,\n preprocessing, and analytics to support model development.\n Contribute to building scalable\n solutions on Cloud and Data Platforms (AWS/Azure/GCP).\n Collaborate with cross-functional\n teams to integrate AI solutions into applications.\n Stay updated with emerging\n technologies in AI, Machine Learning, and Data Engineering.\n\n \n\nRequired Skills:\n\n Strong foundation in Mathematics,\n Statistics, and Probability.\n Proficiency in Python or other\n programming languages used in AI and Data Science.\n Familiarity with AI/ML frameworks\n Understanding of Cloud Platforms\n (AWS, Azure, GCP) and Data Platforms.\n Strong problem-solving, analytical,\n and logical thinking abilities.\n Ability to\n work on a dynamic, research-oriented team that has concurrent projects\n\n \n\nEligibility:\n\n B.E./B.Tech\n (Computer Science, IT, Data Science, AI, or related fields).\n\nSelection Process:\n\n Online Aptitude & Technical Test\n Technical Interview\n HR Interview\n\nWe look forward to welcoming you to this exciting\njourney of learning and innovation!",
