			"IDFC FIRST Bank's core philosophy follows a customer centric promise\nAlways You First. The bank aspires to provide high quality financial solutions\nfor emerging India, while keeping customer at the core. \n\nAbout your future dream team\n\nOur team is pivotal for delivering the\nvision – Always You First. This team acts as a center of excellence to provide\naccurate and timely insights and data driven solutions to drive personalized\nand innovative product offerings to our customers. \n\nAt IDFC First bank, we know that not\neveryone can bring all the skills & experiences to the table, therefore, we\nare more focused on people bringing a growth mindset to their approach to work.\nLearning on the job is the way we work, so don’t worry if don’t have all! \n\nWe work closely with all business units\n(product, sales), functional stakeholders (e.g. credit, operations, Journey\nExcellence), technology teams (IT team and vendors) and external partners (e.g.\nDSAs, agencies) to create and deliver competitive advantage and quantifiable\nimpact on the Bank’s performance. \n\nAlso, to add, we not only work with\ntraditional data environment of relational databases, SQL/SAS but also in AWS\nusing PySpark, Sagemaker and other Auto – ML tools like Altair.\n\nThe Purpose\n\nThe Data Science role\n\nq Identifies business needs\n\nq Builds advanced analytical ML & DL models and tools\n\nq Develop test strategies\n\nq Supports Senior Scientist & Lead Scientist in delivering\nbusiness outcomes\n\n \n\nAreas that play to your strengths\n\nq Identify and scope business requirements and priorities through\nrigorous information gathering and analysis as well as clarification of the\nsolutions, initiatives and programs to enable effective delivery.\n\nq Design models to meet current and future business needs.\n\nq Solid understanding of data and fields required for analysis\n\nq Use advanced AI/ML techniques to solve different business problems\n\nq Develop a test strategy and systematic test procedures to verify and\nensure that solution meets its design specifications\n\nq Develop, select and apply algorithms and advanced computational\nmethods to enable systems to learn, improve, adapt and produce desired outcomes\nor tasks.\n\n \n\n \n\nThings we’ll like about you!\n\nq You love problem solving, you have excellent communication skills\nand you are action oriented (you like doing stuff, not just thinking or talking\nabout them)\n\nq You can work with unstructured problem statements (like estimating\nhow many square feet of pizza is consumed in India in a day without looking it\nup on the internet)\n\nq You get excited at the prospect of working with large volumes of\ndata and enjoy coding!\n\nq You are open to learning continuously – irrespective of whether it\nis a new technology, a new algorithm or a new business!\n\nq You know when to look things up on the internet!",
