		details:
			"Key Responsibilities\n\n \n\n Design, prototype, and implement runtime security\n modules for AI/LLM systems.\n Develop, test attack simulations using OWASP Top\n 10 and MITRE Attack lists.\n Design and develop guard railing strategies for\n AI/LLM models.\n Work hands-on with AI model platforms (Hugging\n Face, Langhian, OpenAI, Ollama) to build and secure pipelines.\n Deploy and optimize security solutions on cloud\n environments (AWS, GCP, Azure) using tools like Docker, Kubernetes,\n SageMaker, or Kubeflow.\n Build Python-based APIs, monitoring tools, and\n anomaly detection scripts for runtime protection.\n Collaborate with other engineering teams to\n harden AI applications.\n\n \n\nRequired Skills\n\n \n\n Deep Knowledge on AI/ML concepts.\n Strong hands-on Python coding and debugging\n skills.\n Experience with AI/ML development frameworks\n (PyTorch, TensorFlow, Hugging Face).\n Familiarity with LLMs and orchestration\n frameworks (Langchain, RAG pipelines).\n Exposure to cloud platforms (AWS/GCP/Azure) and\n containerization tools (Docker, Kubernetes).\n Good understanding of AI safety & security\n concepts (adversarial ML, runtime attacks, prompt injection).\n Knowledge of OWASP AI Top 10, MITRE ATT&CK\n for AI (preferred).\n Strong problem-solving mindset, ability to work\n in fast-paced, hands-on engineering environments.",
		info: "At Protectt.ai, we’re not just building security\nproducts - we’re shaping the future of mobile and AI security. In just 5\nyears, we’ve become India’s leading Mobile Threat Defense (MTD) platform,\nprotecting millions of users across banking, fintech, insurance, and more. Now,\nwe’re taking it global - expanding into the UAE, US, and APAC and\nventuring into the next frontier: AI Security. From securing mobile apps\nto defending AI models and LLMs, we’re on the bleeding edge of\ncybersecurity innovation.\n\n🚀 Why Join Us?\n\n 🧠 Work\n on Cutting-Edge Tech\n Be part of a team building AI security tools, adversarial defense systems,\n and real-time threat detection platforms.\n 🌍 Global\n Exposure\n Collaborate with teams across India, UAE, and the US as we scale\n internationally.\n 🧪 Innovation\n Center in Chennai\n Our R&D hub is where ideas turn into patented products. You’ll work\n alongside top minds in cybersecurity and AI.\n 💼 Fast-Track\n Career Growth\n Join a high-growth startup backed by Bessemer Venture Partners and Bajaj\n Finance with real ownership and impact from Day 1.\n 🛡️ Employee\n Benefits\n \n Flexible\n work culture\n Learning\n & development support\n Wellness\n initiatives, medical insurance and more\n \n 🏆 Award-Winning\n Culture\n Recognized as Cybersecurity Company of the Year and Security\n Product Innovator - we’re proud of our work and the people behind it.\n\n👩‍💻 Who We’re\nLooking For:\n\nSmart, curious, and driven individuals who want to build,\nbreak, and secure the future of tech. Whether you're into AI,\ncybersecurity, or full-stack development there’s a place for you here.",
