		details:
			"Company Overview:ARCON is a globally recognized Identity-As-A-Service provider with a wealth of experience in risk \nmanagement and continuous risk assessment tools committed to excellence, innovation, and security. \nOur award-winning solutions portfolio includes our Privileged Access Management (PAM) solution \nalong with Identity and Access Management (IAM), Endpoint Privilege Management (EPM), and Cloud \nGovernance (CIEM), among others. Our world-class training, deployment, and support help \norganizations optimize their experience with our solutions right from the procurement stage and \nconfigure our solutions to match all challenges to support growth and scalability. ARCON is a leading \ncybersecurity organization, and we pride ourselves on fostering a culture of continuous learning and \nprofessional development.Must Have: .NET C#, ASP. Net, Win Forms, SQL Server, and Web services\nAdditional Skill Set: Windows Services, Security Domain, Requirement Gathering, Analysis, and \nProblem Solving.Website: http://www.arconnet.comLocation: MumbaiWe are looking for an enthusiastic and motivated .NET Developer (Fresher) to join our development team. This is an excellent opportunity to start your career in software development, working on real-world projects with exposure to full-stack development, client interaction, and project management practices.\nIf you have academic or self-taught experience in Data Structures, Algorithms, and Multithreading, that will be considered a strong added advantage.Key Responsibilities:Assist in the design and development of applications using the .NET framework\n\nSupport modifications and improvements to existing applications\n\nCollaborate with senior developers and participate in code reviews and team meetings\n\nLearn and understand the logic, flow, and business purpose behind applications\n\nCreate and update databases using SQL and other modern database tools\n\nSupport in the development and maintenance of RESTful APIs\n\nParticipate in requirement gathering and client meetings (including on-site, if needed)\n\nTake ownership of assigned tasks and deliver them within deadlineAdditionally (Good to Have)Knowledge or experience with Data Structures & Algorithms\n\nExperience with multithreading in real-world applications\n\nExposure to modern database technologies like NoSQL\n\nFamiliarity with Agile development practices",
