			"Ssquad Ventures is a squad of leading family\noffices converging with a unified mission to elevate the student entrepreneurial\nlandscape and effect transformative change. Led by the 4,000 crore Pokarna\nFamily Office since 2024, Ssquad Ventures has been venture building in sectors\nsuch as Ai, Fintech, Social Commerce & Gaming. Currently Hiring for Inplayin\n(www.inplayin.com) Wholifyy & 2 Ventures in Stealth\n(Social Commerce & Ecommerce) \nJob Description As a UI/UX & Creative Designer; You will combine UI/UX design with\ncreative storytelling to shape product interfaces, brand identity, and multimedium content across multiple ventures. Roles & Responsibilities 1. Product & UI/UX Design • Design intuitive, modern, high-impact interfaces for web & mobile\nproducts. • Create wireframes, prototypes, design systems, UI kits, and pixel-perfect\nscreens. • Collaborate with product, engineering, and founders to ensure smooth\ndelivery and high-quality user experiences. • Conduct or participate in user research, testing, and data-driven UX\nimprovements. • Contribute to cross-venture design systems used by multiple products\nunder Ssquad Ventures.2. Creativity, Content & Storytelling\n• Support and lead promo shoots, including moodboards, art direction, shot\nplanning, and production support. • Create short-form videos, UI motion animations, reels, teasers, product\ndemos, brand storytelling edits. • Design social media creatives, campaigns, posters, ads, brand assets,\npitch decks & marketing visuals. • Work with marketing and founders to craft consistent brand identity &\nvisual direction across mediums. • Conceptualize creative ideas for product launches, pitch presentations,\nevents, and campaigns.3. Cross-Team Collaboration • Work directly with founders, product managers, engineers, and marketing\nteams. • Participate in brainstorming, product strategy discussions, and creative\ninnovation sessions. • Help build design culture, processes, and documentation across the\nventure ecosystem.Professional & Technical Skills\n• 1–3 years of experience OR exceptional fresh talent with a strong\nportfolio.\n• Strong command over Figma + familiarity with creative tools\n(Photoshop, Illustrator, Premiere Pro, After Effects, CapCut, etc.).\n• Passion for visual design, branding, interface design, and creative\ncontent.\n• Ability to balance clean UI thinking with creative storytelling.\n• Someone ambitious, detail-oriented, and excited about working on\nmultiple products simultaneously.\n• A mindset of ownership, learning, experimentation, and rapid iteration.What You’ll Gain At Ssquad, designers are not just designers — they are creative leaders shaping\nmultiple venture journeys. You’ll get: • Full ownership of design across AI, Gaming, HealthTech, FinTech, D2C,\nSocial Commerce ventures. • Massive exposure to 0-to-1 product building, brand creation, and\nstorytelling. • Mentorship directly from founders & senior product leaders.\n• A fast-paced, high-creativity, startup ecosystem. • Chance to build a portfolio spanning UI/UX, branding, motion design,\ncampaigns, and product shoots.\nAdditional Details\nCTC : 10L+ Additional Perks: Free Shared Accommodation Provided in Mumbai Region",
		info: "At Ssquad Ventures, your UI/UX interview will be conducted by a diverse team with product experience across IoT, Ecommerce, EdTech, Healthcare, and Consumer Apps. We value designers who combine strong UX fundamentals with refined UI craft and the ability to think creatively across mediums. A well-diversified portfolio—showing user flows, visual design, motion/brand work, and real problem-solving—will help you stand out. Please be prepared to walk us through 2–3 key projects, explain your design decisions clearly, and demonstrate versatility in how you approach different product types. Our environment is fast-paced and multi-vertical, so we look for designers who can adapt quickly, design with clarity, and bring fresh creative thinking to every brief.",
