		details:
			"Role Overview\nAs an Analyst, you will work closely with senior bankers and clients across the entire deal life cycle. This role \ncombines rigorous financial analysis with direct involvement in client and investor interactions, offering a strong \nplatform to build a career in investment banking.Key Responsibilities for an Analyst\n• Prepare deal materials: information memoranda, presentations, and financial models • Support execution: launch, investor outreach, due diligence, and closure • Conduct detailed financial analysis on Excel and develop presentations on PowerPoint • Contribute to addressing investor queries and participate in client meetings • Manage multiple stakeholders with confidence and precision We are looking for students with - • Strong analytical skills and structured problem-solving ability • Knowledge of financial concepts and fundamentals of corporate finance, ability to assimilate & articulate \nfinancial and business information efficiently • Strong working knowledge of MS Office tools (Excel, PowerPoint, Word). • Confidence in handling client and investor interactions.If you are keen to build a career in investment banking and thrive in a high-performance environment - apply now and \nbe part of o3 Capital’s journey.",
