		details:
			"Position: Data Scientist \n\nExperience: 0-1 Year\n\nLocation: Delhi / Kolkata (with flexibility for hybrid working)\n\nJob Type: Full time\n\nDate of Joining:\n1st September\n2026\n\nAbout Us:\n\nAt Aria Intelligent Solutions, we are committed to building the next generation of data science\nleaders. We founded Aria with the simple goal of challenging the status\nquo by providing expert advice and specialist\nskills delivered by experienced teams,\nin an agile way, and at a fair price. As a global leader in consulting and professional services, we blend deep business expertise with advanced analytics to help clients solve their most complex challenges. We are looking\nfor bright, analytical minds eager to launch their data science careers with\nus.\n\nPosition Overview:\n\n We’re\nlooking for ambitious graduate\ndata scientists with\nsharp logical thinking,\nproficient Python programming skills,\na strong grasp of machine\nlearning concepts, and a deep foundation in probability\nand statistics. This is a unique opportunity to join a high-performing AI team, collaborate with industry\nleaders, and grow in a structured environment that values continuous learning and real-world impact.\n\nEducational Qualifications:\n\n· \nMTech/MCA, Mathematics, Statistics, Computer Science, or related fields.\n\n· \nStrong academic grounding in probability, statistics, and quantitative methods is essential.\n\n· \nKnowledge of AI and Machine Learning\nand its core concepts.\n\n \n\nYour Key Responsibilities:\n\n· \nCollaborate with senior data scientists and consultants to address real-world business challenges\nusing analytics and machine learning.\n\n· \nApply your statistical knowledge and coding skills\nto build and evaluate\npredictive models.\n\n· \nAssist in designing, training,\nand evaluating ML models (e.g., regression, classification, clustering) using Python\nlibraries (Scikit-learn, XGBoost).\n\n· \nAssist in data cleaning, processing, and transformation using Python\n\n· \nContribute to the development of client deliverables.\n\n· \nPresent findings\nto stakeholders through\npresentations, visualizations (Matplotlib, Seaborn) and reports.\n\n· \nStay\ncurrent with emerging\ntrends in Data\nScience and Artificial Intelligence.\n\n· \nEngage in firm-wide\nlearning programs and actively seek mentorship and feedback.\n\n \n\nSkills & Attributes We Look For:\n\n· \nStrong logical reasoning\nand critical thinking\nskills.\n\n· \nProficient in Python for data\nanalysis (pandas, NumPy, scikit-learn).\n\n· \nStrong foundation in statistics\nand probability theory.\n\n· \nFamiliarity with basic machine learning\nconcepts (regression, classification, clustering).\n\n· \nExcellent communication and presentation skills.\n\n· \nEagerness to learn, adapt,\nand grow in a dynamic\nteam environment.\n\n \n\nWhat We Offer:\n\n· Global Exposure\n\no \nWork with diverse teams and clients\nfrom multiple industries and geographies.\n\n· Structured Career Growth\n\no \nClear career pathways\nwith defined milestones and promotion opportunities.\n\n· World-Class Learning\n& Development\n\no \nAccess to proprietary learning platforms, certification support, and mentorship\nprograms.\n\no \nGet\ntrained on cloud technologies (Azure, AWS), machine\nlearning frameworks, and BI\ntools.\n\n· Mentorship & Support\n\no One-on-one mentoring by experienced data science\nprofessionals and regular feedback sessions.\n\n· Rewards & Recognition\n\no \nPerformance-based bonuses, awards, and appreciation programs.\n\n· Holistic Benefits\n\no \nCompetitive\ncompensation package\n\no \nMedical insurance\nfor you and your family\n\no \nEmployee wellness programs\n\no \nHybrid working opportunities\n\no \nAccess to mental\nhealth and counselling services\n\n· Fast-Track Your Data Science Career\n\no \nOpportunity to\nwork on cutting-edge projects that make\nreal business impact.\n\no Build a strong\nfoundation and transition into specialized roles in machine\nlearning, AI, or analytics consulting.",
