		details:
			"Founder's Office – Strategic AssociateLocation: Bhopal / Hybrid flexibilityAbout We360.ai:We360.ai is a leading SaaS-based Employee Monitoring and Productivity Platform trusted by 5000+companies across industries. As a rapidly growing tech startup, we are on a mission to redefineworkforce analytics and productivity using cutting-edge technology and intuitive design.Role Overview:We are hiring a highly driven, analytical, and entrepreneurial individual to join the Founder’s Office.This is a high-impact role that offers a 360-degree view of a fast-scaling SaaS company. You will workdirectly with the Founder and leadership team on strategic projects, cross-functional initiatives,investor relations, business growth, and decision-making support. This role is ideal for ambitiousIIT/IIM grads who aspire to build or lead a business in the near future.Key Responsibilities: Strategic Planning: Support the Founder in driving company strategy, identifying newgrowth opportunities, and executing key business initiatives. Investor Relations: Assist in fundraising activities, preparing investor decks, marketresearch, and competitive analysis. Business Operations: Solve high-priority operational problems, create dashboards andframeworks to streamline internal processes. Special Projects: Own and execute projects across sales, marketing, product, partnerships,and HR. Analytics & Insights: Analyze data to provide actionable insights, performance tracking, andreporting to aid strategic decisions. Stakeholder Management: Coordinate with internal and external stakeholders to ensuretimely execution of initiatives.Who Should Apply:We are looking for top-tier talent from IITs/IIMs with: 2–3 years of experience in consulting, product, business strategy, startup, or founder's officeroles Strong problem-solving and analytical skills Excellent communication and stakeholder management abilities Hunger to learn, willingness to hustle, and readiness to take ownership A bias for action, agility, and high adaptability in a fast-paced environmentWhy Join Us? Direct exposure to startup leadership and end-to-end business operations Steep learning curve with real decision-making responsibilities Opportunity to work on zero-to-one initiatives and shape the next growth phase ofWe360.ai Fast-track career growth in the startup ecosystem Be part of a mission-driven team solving the future of work",
		info: "Perks Beyond the Compensation Package\nAt We360.ai, we believe that growth goes beyond paychecks. Apart from a competitive compensation package, you’ll enjoy:\n\nPerformance-based Incentives: Rewarding innovation, ownership, and impactful contributions.\n\nFlexible Work Culture: Hybrid and remote work options for better work-life balance.\n\nContinuous Learning Opportunities: Sponsored certifications, internal knowledge sessions, and mentorship from industry experts.\n\nEmployee Wellness Benefits: Access to fitness programs, mental health support, and recreational initiatives.\n\nCareer Acceleration: Fast-track growth opportunities for high-performing individuals.\n\nAbout Our Company Culture\nWe360.ai fosters a culture of curiosity, ownership, and collaboration. Our teams work with agility, experiment boldly, and celebrate both effort and achievement. We promote transparency in communication, value every idea, and encourage cross-functional learning.\nAt We360.ai, you’ll find yourself in an environment that:\n\nValues innovation over hierarchy\n\nEncourages open conversations and idea sharing\n\nBelieves in people-first leadership\n\nNurtures a growth mindset and continuous improvement\n\nTraining and Development Facilities\nWe ensure every new team member transitions smoothly from campus to corporate through our Structured Training and Mentorship Program, which includes:\n\nComprehensive Onboarding: Introduction to products, business functions, and company systems.\n\nTechnical & Functional Training: Hands-on learning modules to strengthen domain expertise.\n\nSoft Skills Development: Communication, teamwork, and leadership workshops.\n\nMentorship Support: One-on-one guidance from senior leaders to help shape your professional journey.\n\nGuidance for the Screening Process\nTo help you prepare better, here’s what we recommend:\n\nUnderstand Our Product: Visit we360.ai to explore what we do and how we help businesses boost productivity.\n\nStrengthen Your Core Skills: Be confident in your technical fundamentals and problem-solving abilities.\n\nPractice Aptitude & Logical Reasoning: These play a key role in our screening assessments.\n\nShowcase Your Passion: During interviews, highlight your curiosity, teamwork, and readiness to learn.\n\nBe Yourself: We value authenticity and potential as much as skills.",
