		details:
			"Key Responsibilities: ● Assist in developing AI agents (reasoning, memory, learning, planning, collaboration, \nguard railing) for the MySellerCentral AI Factory. ● Contribute to: \n○ Content generation, grading, and enhancement \n○ Sales forecasting and inventory optimization \n○ Customer sentiment analysis from feedback and reviews \n○ Competition mapping across listings, pricing, ratings, and keywords ● Work with structured/unstructured datasets for data cleaning, feature extraction, and \nEDA. ● Build and test models using Python, scikit-learn, PyTorch, TensorFlow, Hugging \nFace, and LangChain. ● Explore voice AI (ASR/TTS) and computer vision use cases (e.g., Stable \nDiffusion-based image generation). ● Support prompt design, embedding pipelines, and retrieval-augmented generation \n(RAG) systems. ● Document experiments, results, and model behaviors with clarity and consistency.",
		info: "Company Overview: \nAt MySellerCentral, we are building an AI-first platform to transform how sellers grow in the \ndigital marketplace. Our intelligent systems power the entire lifecycle of e-commerce—from \ncontent generation, grading, and enhancement, to sales forecasting, inventory \noptimization, marketing analytics, customer sentiment analysis, and competition tracking. \nNow, we are initiating the development of a modular AI Factory—a dynamic ecosystem of \nautonomous agents capable of reasoning, learning, remembering, planning, collaborating, \nand operating under guardrails. This foundation will drive real-time, intelligent \ndecision-making across every workflow.",
