		details:
			"About Giga:At Giga, we’re shaping the future of conversational AI, fully automating customer support to enterprise-grade levels with a lean team of exceptional engineers. Our customers trust our agents to navigate complex, real-world conversations with clarity, accuracy, and scalability. We’ve deployed AI agents that resolve over 1 million support tickets monthly for a single customer.Today, we work with some of the most recognizable names in food delivery and crypto, rapidly establishing ourselves as a frontrunner in the space. With multi-year contracts across industries and We recently closed our $61M Series A and are expanding our engineering team, We’re on track to power the next trillion voice interactions. globally.CTC: $150,000 base + $120,000 stock (over 4 years) + $30,000 annual bonusLocation: In office (San Francisco)Why Join UsMomentum: Join a team validated by both customers and investorsOwnership: Contribute to cutting-edge ML projects and shape our technical directionGrowth: Work alongside top-tier engineers and founders on ambitious, global productsAbout the RoleWe’re seeking a Software Engineer with hands-on experience building and deploying LLM-based products from scratch. You should take pride in writing high-quality, scalable code and thrive in a fast-paced, high-ownership environment.What You’ll Do• Ship and own products — contribute rapidly and eventually lead your own product lines• Design scalable solutions that remain fast, reliable, and secure as we grow• Translate vision into execution — work with founders to turn ideas into impactful launchesWho You Are / Must-Haves• Backend: Strong Python skills (Django experience is a plus)• Frontend: Proficiency in Next.js, React, and ShadCN• Cloud: Comfortable with AWS or Google Cloud• Scalability: Familiarity with Kubernetes and Docker is a plus• Mindset: High grit and a bias for ownership and long-hour productivity",
