		details:
			"Role: Software Development Engineer - ILocation: Bangalore, IndiaEngineering - Full time /On-siteEligibility criteria:B Tech in Computer Science or equivalent degree CGPA of 8 and aboveAbout Hevo: Ever wondered, what’s common between Zepto, Napster, Curefit, Groww, Jumio, Cars24? They all super-charge their business growth with Hevo Data Pipelines. How? 2 of every 3 modern day companies are unable to take data driven decision making due to fragmented data across 100s of business software. Hevo is a simple, intuitive, and powerful No-code Data Pipeline platform that enables companies to consolidate data from multiple software for faster analytics. For the past 7 years, Hevo’s mission has been simple, but bold: Build technology from India, for the world that is simple to adopt and easy to access so that everyone can unlock the potential of data. Not convincing enough? Let’s make it more exciting. We deal with more than 300 billion events on a monthly basis. These are generated by 2000+ customers spread across 65+ countries. Brands like Zepto, Napster, Curefit, Groww, Jumio, Cars24 rely on Hevo Data for all their data needs.To know more about Hevo, please visit the website. What you’ll own as SDE - I at Hevo:Work on highly maintainable and efficient components/systems.Excelling as an individual contributorIdentify and resolve performance and scalability issues with an increasingly complex enterprise productImproving the overall quality of code structure and productMaintaining the documentation of the particular component you are working onWhy choose Hevo?Hevo is a workplace where you get complete ownership of your goals and your growthAt Hevo, you get an unparalleled environment that welcomes your ideas, thoughts, and opinionsYou get to work with an awesome team that’ll help you learn and grow while delivering resultsBenefits and Perks:Relocation AllowanceCafeteria ServicesValet Parking",
