		details:
			"Salescode.ai is building the future of intelligent sales agents—and we’re looking for a Software Engineer\nwho thrives on solving hard engineering problems and writing exceptional code. In this role, you’ll be\ninstrumental in developing production-grade, scalable systems. While prior GenAI experience is a bonus, we care more about strong backend/full-stack problem solvers\nwho are excited to build next-gen AI systems from scratch and ship scalable Agentic AI products\nImportant: This role is not for candidates who build GenAI agents using plug-and-play tools alone\n(dragand-drop builders, etc.). We’re looking for engineers who deeply understand system architecture,\nLLM workflows, reasoning pipelines, and can build the stack—not just stitch it together. Key Responsibilities • Contribute to the development of Agentic AI systems, including co-pilots, chatbots, and tool-using\nautonomous agents. • Work with senior engineers to build and maintain backend components and APIs that power real-time\nAI products. • Integrate tools like LlamaIndex, LangChain, and vector search systems into production applications. • Assist in deploying and optimizing AI agent pipelines using AWS, Azure, or other cloud environments. • Collaborate with cross-functional teams including ML engineers, product managers, and designers to\nturn ideas into working software. • Write clean, maintainable code and participate in code reviews, testing, and documentation efforts.",
