			"Software Engineer Location: Pune, India (Hybrid) Department: Engineering Employment Type: Full-timeAbout FloQastFloQast is a fast-growing, global B2B SaaS company focused on helping finance and accounting teams close their books faster and more accurately. Our AI-powered platform simplifies workflows, improves collaboration, and delivers real-time insights — trusted by 2,500+ accounting teams worldwide. At FloQast, innovation, teamwork, and continuous learning are at the heart of everything we do.Role OverviewWe are seeking passionate and motivated Software Engineer I graduates to join our high-impact product engineering teams. You will contribute to building modern, scalable, and secure enterprise products used by top global organizations. Expect to learn fast, collaborate deeply, and ship meaningful code from day one.What You’ll DoDesign, develop, test, and maintain high-quality software features and servicesContribute to backend, frontend, or full-stack development depending on team needsWrite clean, scalable, and well-documented code following best engineering practicesDebug and troubleshoot issues across application componentsWork closely with Product, QA, UX, and DevOps to deliver high-impact product enhancementsParticipate in code reviews and continually improve code quality and performanceStay curious — evaluate new tools, technologies, and processes that improve product excellenceWhat We’re Looking ForBachelor’s or Master’s degree in Computer Science, Engineering, or related field (2025 graduates)Strong computer science fundamentals: data structures, algorithms, OS, and networkingHands-on project or internship experience with Java, Golang, or JavaScript/TypeScriptUnderstanding of relational databases (e.g., PostgreSQL, MS SQL, MySQL)Solid problem-solving skills and a passion for building customer-focused softwareExcellent communication and willingness to learn and collaborate in a fast-paced environmentWhy Join FloQast?Opportunity to work with a leading product in the finance automation spaceCulture built on trust, collaboration, and innovationMentorship, career development, and continuous learning programsCompetitive compensation and employee benefitsWork on cutting-edge technologies powering global scale",
