		details:
			"Join Plivo as an AI/ML Engineer – Bangalore (Work from Office) About PlivoPlivo powers intelligent customer engagement for some of the world’s biggest B2C brands including Uber, WhatsApp, and Zomato. Our AI Agents Platform automates the entire customer lifecycle from acquisition to support using cutting-edge multimodal AI that blends LLMs, speech-to-text, text-to-speech, and real-time voice intelligence.We operate at a global scale, handling over 1 billion+ API requests every month.Now, we’re looking for the brightest AI/ML minds to help us push the boundaries of real-time AI systems.The RoleAs an AI/ML Engineer at Plivo, you’ll be hands-on with production-grade AI building, training, and deploying models that power real-time voice and language experiences for millions of users. You’ll work closely with product and engineering teams to bring AI research to life, at scale. This isn’t a research internship - it’s a high-impact, build-from-Day-1 kind of role.What You’ll DoTrain, fine-tune, and deploy speech, NLP, and voice automation models - think ASR, speaker isolation, and turn detection.Build scalable inference pipelines that deliver millisecond-level performance.Optimize models for accuracy, latency, and throughput — because this is real-time AI.Analyze large-scale datasets, surface insights, and iterate fast.Work cross-functionally with data, infra, and product teams to take models to production.Experiment with the latest in LLMs, generative AI, and multimodal frameworks always staying ahead of the curve.What We’re Looking ForB.Tech/M.Tech in CS, AI/ML, Data Science, or related field - preferably from a top engineering school.Strong fundamentals in ML, DL, and model training.Proficiency in Python and frameworks like PyTorch, TensorFlow, or Hugging Face.Hands-on experience with NLP, ASR, TTS, embeddings, or voice agents (Kaggle/competition wins are a plus).Solid skills in data processing, feature engineering, and evaluation.A curious mind, a builder’s attitude, and clear communication skills.Bonus PointsExperience deploying models in real-time or large-scale systems.Familiarity with ML Ops pipelines.Exposure to speech, voice, or multimodal datasets.Contributions to open-source ML projects.Build something end-to-end from scratch.Why PlivoBuild AI that actually ships - powering real products used by global brands.Work with massive, real-world speech and language datasets.Thrive in a high-ownership, no-handholding engineering culture.Be at the intersection of real-time systems and AI - a rare, exciting space.Join a team that values innovation, experimentation, and impact over hierarchy.",
