		details:
			"Role\nOverview\n\nJoin Tanla’s cutting-edge Data Science Team, where innovation\nmeets scale. You’ll work with massive datasets across messaging, telecom, and\nenterprise communication, building AI-powered models that impact millions of\nusers in real time.\n\nIf you’re passionate about Machine Learning, AI, NLP, and Big Data, this is\nyour opportunity to build and deploy production-scale intelligence systems from\nDay 1.\n\nAs a Data Science Engineer at Tanla, you will:\n\n· \nExplore and analyze data: Collect,\nclean, and visualize large-scale datasets to uncover trends, patterns, and\nactionable insights.\n\n· \nEngineer features: Design meaningful data\ntransformations and feature sets that enhance model accuracy and robustness.\n\n· \nBuild predictive models: Develop\nand experiment with ML models for prediction, optimization, and self-learning\napplications.\n\n· \nWork on NLP & LLM projects: Build\nand fine-tune text intelligence models for intent detection, message routing,\nsummarization, and generative AI use cases.\n\n· \nEvaluate and fine-tune models: Assess\nmodel performance using key metrics, and fine-tune them to customize\nAI solutions for specific business use cases and\nreal-world scenarios.\n\n· \nDeploy and monitor models: Take\nmodels to real-world production using scalable APIs, automation workflows, and\nreal-time data pipelines.\n\n· \nCollaborate cross-functionally: Work\nclosely with product, engineering, and business teams to translate data-driven\ninsights into impactful decisions and features.\n\n \n\nWho Can Apply\n\n· \nStrong fundamentals in Statistics, Probability, Linear Algebra,\nand Machine Learning.\n\n· \nProficiency in Python and exposure to data handling (NumPy,\nPandas, SQL).\n\n· \nFamiliarity with ML algorithms, model evaluation, and exploratory\ndata analysis.\n\n· \nPassion for solving real-world problems using AI and innovation.\n\nPreferred (Good to Have)\n\n· \nProjects in AI / ML / NLP / GenAI / LLMs (academic or personal).\n\n· \nUnderstanding of the telecom or enterprise communication domain\n(optional) is a plus.\n\nWhy join us?\n\n· \nImpactful Work: Solve meaningful real-life\nbusiness problems by building cutting-edge products.\n\n· \nTremendous Growth Opportunities: Work in a\nfast-growing CPaaS and product-driven culture with scope for continuous\nprofessional development.\n\n· \nInnovative Environment: Be part of a\nworld-class team that loves solving tough problems and values innovation.\n\nTanla is an equal opportunity employer. We champion diversity and\nare committed to creating an inclusive environment for all employees.",
