			"Thermal\nSystems Design Engineer\n\nAbout\nPromethean Energy\n\nPromethean Energy is at the forefront of\nindustrial decarbonization in India, specializing in innovative heat recovery\nsystems and heat pump solutions. Founded by IIT Bombay graduates, we have\nsuccessfully reduced over 1 million tonnes of CO2 emissions in the past decade.\nOur mission is to revolutionize industrial energy efficiency through\ncutting-edge thermal engineering solutions.\n\nRole\nOverview\n\nWe are seeking an exceptional B.Tech/M.Tech\ngraduate in Thermal Engineering or Design Engineering to join our dynamic team\nas a Thermal Systems Design Engineer. This role offers a unique opportunity to\nbe directly involved in designing and manufacturing next-generation heat\nrecovery and heat pump systems that are transforming India's industrial\nlandscape.\n\nKey\nResponsibilities\n\n Design\n and develop innovative thermal systems, including heat pumps and heat\n recovery solutions\n Participate\n in the complete product development cycle from concept to manufacturing\n Perform\n thermal calculations, system modeling, and optimization\n Collaborate\n with cross-functional teams to ensure manufacturing feasibility\n Conduct\n thermal performance analysis and efficiency optimization\n Support\n on-site system implementation and troubleshooting\n Contribute\n to research and development of new thermal technologies\n\nRequired\nQualifications\n\n B.Tech/M.Tech\n in Thermal Engineering or Design Engineering (Fresh graduates welcome)\n Strong\n fundamental understanding of: \n \n Heat\n transfer principles\n Thermodynamics\n Refrigeration\n cycles\n Fluid\n mechanics\n \n Proficiency\n in thermal system design and analysis\n Knowledge\n of industry standards and best practices\n Excellent\n analytical and problem-solving skills\n\nDesired\nQualities\n\n Independent\n worker with strong initiative\n Quick\n learner with exceptional aptitude for technical concepts\n Innovative\n mindset with passion for sustainable technology\n Strong\n communication and documentation skills\n Ability\n to work effectively in a fast-paced startup environment\n\nWhy Join\nUs?\n\n Industry-leading\n compensation package\n Opportunity\n to work directly with experienced founders from IIT Bombay\n Flexible\n work environment that encourages innovation\n Direct\n impact on India's industrial decarbonization efforts\n Rapid\n career growth potential in a fast-growing company\n Hands-on\n experience with cutting-edge thermal technologies\n Mentorship\n from industry experts\n Collaborative\n and learning-focused culture\n\nCompensation\n\n Competitive based on performance and candidate.\n\nWork\nEnvironment\n\n Dynamic\n startup culture with flat hierarchy\n Direct\n access to leadership team\n Focus\n on innovation and continuous learning\n State-of-the-art\n design and manufacturing facilities\n Regular\n knowledge sharing and training sessions\n\nImpact\n\nJoin us in our mission to revolutionize\nindustrial energy efficiency in India. Your work will directly contribute to\nreducing carbon emissions and promoting sustainable industrial practices across\nthe country.",
		info: "Why Join\nUs?\n\n Industry-leading\n compensation package\n Opportunity\n to work directly with experienced founders from IIT Bombay\n Flexible\n work environment that encourages innovation\n Direct\n impact on India's industrial decarbonization efforts\n Rapid\n career growth potential in a fast-growing company\n Hands-on\n experience with cutting-edge thermal technologies\n Mentorship\n from industry experts\n Collaborative\n and learning-focused culture\n\nCompensation\n\n Competitive based on performance and candidate.\n\nWork\nEnvironment\n\n Dynamic\n startup culture with flat hierarchy\n Direct\n access to leadership team\n Focus\n on innovation and continuous learning\n State-of-the-art\n design and manufacturing facilities\n Regular\n knowledge sharing and training sessions\n\nImpact\n\nJoin us in our mission to revolutionize\nindustrial energy efficiency in India. Your work will directly contribute to\nreducing carbon emissions and promoting sustainable industrial practices across\nthe country.",
