		reqs: "Eligibility Criteria:· Students must have scored at least 65% marks or equivalent CGPA marks in 10th & 12th / Diploma (if applicable) - No rounding off marks is allowed· Students must have scored at least 65% marks aggregate or equivalent CGPA till recent Semester in BE/B.Tech - No rounding off marks is allowed· Students must have scored at least 60% marks aggregate or equivalent CGPA till recent Semester in ME/M.Tech - No rounding off marks is allowed· Only FULL Time and Regular education is eligible (10th/12th/Diploma/B.Tech)Not Eligible:· Students pursuing ME/M.Tech are not being considered· Any education from Distance learning or open school is not considered· Students pursuing dual degree are not being considered· Students with pending back papers are not eligible to participate in the selection process· Students having Vision related issues and/or color blindness problem are not eligible to participate in the selection processJob Details:· Designation: Graduate Engineer Trainee· Location: Gurgaon / Manesar / Rohtak/ Kharkhoda or other any other location PAN India on business needSelection Process:· Online Test (Technical, Aptitude & Psychometric)· Presentation Round and Personal Interview Round (Technical + HR)Tentative Joining in July 2026",
