			"Resume filtering | Technical test (01:20) | Technical interview (00:30) | Personal interview (00:20)",
		details:
			"About Digital and IT Organization-Bajaj Auto is on an exciting journey to strengthen its digital foundation and accelerate innovation through the creation of the Digital & Information Technology Organization (DIO). The DIO integrates Digital & Analytics, MIS, and R&D IT functions into a unified and agile structure enabling a seamless flow of data, insight, and technology across the enterprise. With this integrated setup, the DIO will drive business transformation through advanced digital capabilities, harnessing the power of AI, next-gen platforms, data-driven insights, and modern enterprise architecture. Our vision is to deliver cutting-edge technology solutions that empower innovation, improve efficiency, and enhance the overall customer and business experience.Key ResponsibilitiesAs a Graduate Trainee Engineer (GTE) in Bajaj Auto’s Digital & Information Technology Organization, you will be part of a high-impact team driving the company’s digital transformation journey. You will:➢ Work on technology driven business transformation initiatives that connect digital innovation with real-world impact.➢ Contribute to projects leveraging AI, ML, data analytics, cloud platforms, and automation to enhance enterprise efficiency and scalability.➢ Support the integration of IT systems across R&D, Manufacturing, and Business Functions to ensure data consistency and agility.➢ Collaborate with cross-functional teams to design and deploy digital solutions that improve operational performance and customer experience.➢ Participate in architecture modernization projects, enhancing system reliability, security, and speed.➢ Analyze business problems, recommend digital interventions, and contribute to continuous improvement initiatives.➢ Learn from industry experts and technology leaders, gaining exposure to global best practices in digital transformation.What’s in it for you?➢ Exposure to diverse technologies and real-world projects from day one.➢ Guidance from senior leaders and digital transformation experts across domains.➢ Work in an agile, technology-forward environment that values creativity and experimentation.➢ Collaborate with teams in R&D, Manufacturing, Supply Chain, and Corporate Functions.➢ Be part of initiatives that enhance Bajaj Auto’s global competitiveness and digital excellence.➢ Build a strong foundation for a long-term career in technology, digital strategy, and business transformation.",
