		details:
			"About New Product Development (NPD)At Bajaj Auto, we are building a robust New Product Development (NPD) organization to drive innovation and excellence across our product portfolio. The NPD function aims to redefine how products are conceived, engineered, and launched — ensuring faster development, flawless execution, and consistent delivery of high-quality products to market. This setup is designed to:➢ Integrate Product Design, Engineering, and Front-End Functions for seamless concept-to-market transitions and sharper product strategies.➢ Strengthen Cross-Functional Collaboration, bringing together R&D, Manufacturing, Quality, Service, and vendor partners to ensure efficiency and agility.➢ Enhance Systems and Processes, promoting transparency, accountability, and measurable performance through PQCDSM-driven metrics.➢ Optimize Resources and Improve Throughput, enabling Bajaj Auto to deliver innovative products that meet global standards and customer expectations.➢ Through NPD, we aim to create a more agile, data-driven, and collaborative product ecosystem that accelerates innovation and sustains Bajaj Auto’s market leadership.Key Responsibilities➢ As a Graduate Trainee Engineer in the NPD organization, you will play a pivotal role in shaping the next generation of Bajaj Auto products. Your responsibilities will include:➢ Supporting end-to-end product development, from design conceptualization to product launch.➢ Working with cross-functional teams to streamline coordination between R&D, Manufacturing, Quality, and Supply Chain functions.➢ Assisting in process optimization and system integration to enhance efficiency and reduce development cycle time.➢ Monitoring and analyzing PQCDSM metrics to identify improvement opportunities and track performance outcomes.➢ Engaging in innovation initiatives, contributing ideas and solutions that drive continuous improvement.➢ Collaborating closely with mentors and senior leaders, gaining exposure to strategic projects and decision-making frameworks.What’s in it for you?➢ A structured, high-impact environment that fast-tracks your professional and technical development.➢ Hands-on involvement in projects that directly influence product design, performance, and business outcomes.➢ Continuous learning through guidance from senior leaders and Subject Matter Experts (SMEs).➢ Experience working across multiple domains from engineering and manufacturing to supply chain and quality.➢ Be part of a dynamic ecosystem that encourages experimentation, learning, and creative problem-solving.➢ Develop a holistic understanding of how ideas evolve into world-class products at Bajaj Auto.",
