		details:
			"About the role As a Junior Product Designer at DoubleTick — the flagship enterprise product by Apport Software Solutions Pvt. Ltd. — you will be at the heart of designing user interfaces for a powerful WhatsApp-based Customer Relations and Communication platform used by over 7,000 businesses across 140+ countries. DoubleTick helps sales teams streamline lead management, collaborate more effectively, and drive results — all within the Meta ecosystem.In this role, you’ll be creating low-fidelity mockups, high-fidelity mockups, and conducting usability testing to ensure your designs are both visually appealing and functional while working closely with senior designers, product managers, and engineers to translate briefs into multiple design options, iterate quickly, and ensure a smooth handoff to development.Beyond the product team, you’ll work cross-functionally with customer support, customer success, and marketing teams to ensure the design aligns with both user needs and business goals.Key Responsibilities Design elegant, user-centered solutions that simplify complex workflows into intuitive experiences, for both web and mobile platforms.Design interfaces for all of our platforms translating requirements into multiple visual options.Work closely with senior designers and engineers to contribute to product feature discussions, and ensure seamless design handoff and faithful implementation of design specifications.Conduct usability testing, user interviews, and implement other research methodologies to validate design decisions and improve product experience.Maintain our design system, ensuring consistency across product surfaces while enabling rapid iteration.Communicate design decisions clearly and effectively to stakeholders, using mockups, prototypes, and rational storytelling.Eligibility Criteria Master’s or Bachelor’s degree in Interaction Design, Product Design, HCI,Communication Design or a related discipline.Strong portfolio demonstrating user-centric design thinking, Mobile/Web app interfaces, and a keen eye for usability and aesthetics.Proficiency in Figma, including component libraries, interactive prototypes, and collaborative design workflows.Solid understanding of UX principles, human-centered design, Interaction design methodologies and research methodologies.Excellent communication and presentation skills — conveying design decisions with clarity and confidence.Functional Competencies User Experience Design – Strong foundation in UX principles, user flows, wireframing, and interaction patterns.Visual Design – Sharp visual sensibility with attention to detail, typography, layout, color, and visual hierarchy.Design Systems – Experience in building and maintaining scalable design systems across products.User Research – Ability to plan and execute usability studies, synthesize findings, and apply insights to design.Conversation UX – Familiarity with communications platform design and behavior-driven design.Core Competencies Collaboration – Comfortable working cross-functionally with engineers, product managers, and business teams.Problem Solving – Skilled at breaking down complex challenges into simple, actionable solutions.Communication – Strong verbal and visual communication skills to express design decisions and user insights.Design Mindset – Deep passion for design with a constant drive to learn, stay updated with industry trends, and explore emerging tools, methods, and technologies.Innovation – Continuously seeks new ideas and opportunities to enhance product experience and usability.About Us Apport Software Solutions Pvt. Ltd. is a fast-growing SaaS product company building innovative solutions in the space of conversational commerce. Founded in 2017, we empower global brands to win more customers by combining simplicity with robust technology. Headquartered in Mumbai, India, we’re proudly backed by top-tier investors from Silicon Valley, Info Edge Ventures and BEENEXT Asia. Our products — DoubleTick and QuickSell — are trusted by thousands of businesses across 140+ countries to transform how they sell, communicate, and grow.Our Products DoubleTickDoubleTick is a WhatsApp-based conversational Intelligence and CX Platform designed to unlock the full marketing and sales potential of the WhatsApp Business API. It offers advanced features such as a central team inbox, bulk broadcasting, analytics, commerce and cataloging tools, Voice call routing, role-based access controls, visual chatbot studio and AI integration. Trusted by leading brands like MakeMyTrip, SabyaSachi, CoinDCX, Cars24, Royal Enfield, Tarun Tahiliani, Times Media, GRT Jewellers, Hiranandani Communities, GJEPC India, DE BEERS Group, IDFC First Bank, Malabar Gold & Diamonds, Raheja Developers, Tupperware and more, DoubleTick powers end-to-end sales workflows for enterprise teams operating at scale.QuickSellQuickSell is a sales acceleration commerce suite started in 2017 with the vision to empower businesses to translate conversations into conversions on customer-first channels like WhatsApp through assisted personal commerce. Today over 7000 businesses from 109+ countries all over the world use QuickSell to accelerate the process of sharing complete and accurate product information with customers and various business stakeholders with objectives like dynamic product showcase and ordering booking over WhatsApp.What We Offer A chance to impact thousands of businesses worldwide by shaping tools they use every day.A fast-paced and flexible startup environment that values ownership and agility.A collaborative, design-forward culture that encourages open dialogue and shared growth.Opportunities to work with cutting-edge technologies in conversational commerce and CRM.A team of driven designers, engineers, and product thinkers committed to helping you growprofessionally and do your best work.",
